      %strong -- Please Note --
      %div
        I am on maternity leave as of 10th November 2013 and will not be taking any bookings until I return in mid 2014.
    .header-container
      %header.wrapper.clearfix
        %h1.title Rosemary Janc, Naturopath
        .main-image-container
          .image.image-6
          .image.image-5
          .image.image-4
          .image.image-3
          .image.image-2
          .image.image-1
        %nav
          %ul
            %li
              =link_to 'Home', '/'
              =link_to 'Bio', '/bio.html'
              =link_to 'Testimonials', '/testimonials.html'
              =link_to 'Friends', '/friends.html'
              =link_to 'Book&nbsp;Online', '/booking.html'
    .main-container
      .main.wrapper.clearfix
        %article
          =yield
        %aside
          %h2.phone Ph: 0408 528 014
          %h4 Clinic location
          %p.address
            Level 3, 370 Queens Pde
            North Fitzroy
            Victoria, Australia
            %br
              %a.show-map{:href => "#"} Show on map
          .map.hidden
          %hr
            %p.quote It is my role as a Naturopath to guide you towards better health. By understanding the link between your environment, food and lifestyle choices, I will help you achieve a balance between physical, emotional and spiritual wellbeing.

    .footer-container
      %footer.wrapper
        %ul.clearfix
          %li
            %h4 Rosemary Janc ND
            %p.small B.HSc- Naturopathy, Adv Dip Naturopathy, Adv.Dip Nutrition, Adv.Dip Herbal Medicine. Cert.IV Touch for Health (Kinesiology).
          %li

